node_hello_microros: 运行可以看到有一个hello_microros节点
```
sudo docker run -it --rm -v /dev:/dev -v /dev/shm:/dev/shm --privileged --net=host microros/micro-ros-agent:$ROS_DISTRO serial --dev /dev/ttyUSB0 -v6 

:~$ ros2 node list 
/hello_microros
```

publish_hello_microros：运行可以看到有一个count话题
```
:~$ ros2 node list 
/hello_microros
:~$ ros2 topic list 
/count
/parameter_events
/rosout
:~$ ros2 topic echo /count 
data: 13
---
data: 14
---
data: 15
---
```

esp32订阅led_control，来改变LED状态
```
ros2 topic pub /led_control  std_msgs/msg/Int32 "{data: 0}" --once 
```